snippet.title: Cool Ratchet & Clank 2: Going Commando Trailer
snippet.description:
Edit: The Ratchet & Clank HD Trilogy is coming including this game! - http://www.amazon.co.uk/The-Ratchet-Clank-Trilogy-Classics/dp/B007RE76MM/

I know this is old, but it needs to be on here! Enjoy! Gotta love the music lol

Edit: Thanks to vjpearce - The first part of the music is "Arena Boss", and the second part is the US version's "Megacorp Armoury Interior"
